Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,无生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:01.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,货物是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:07.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:50.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:55.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽这么说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,也许是一种防卫本能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,但具体缘由至今无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:06.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:08.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,那一天在那一个森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:13.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,她叫了我父亲
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:26.82,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:26.82,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的这份躁动  是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:34.58,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:34.58,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像将脸埋入刚洗过的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:41.71,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:41.71,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鸟儿们吟唱着  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:52.77,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:52.77,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论走到哪  这道路都会延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:01.87,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:01.87,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牵手  更像是紧握这手指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:08.64,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:08.64,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:14.00,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:14.00,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空为毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:19.24,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:19.24,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌对面的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:27.68,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:27.68,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}为你指向尽头之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:37.19,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:37.19,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才该说谢谢你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:55.88,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1625.333,1063.067)}幼子和绿岩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类  离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,这座森林不是外人的居所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不是你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,中止你的跟踪  离开森林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:44.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,不能干涉外物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:59.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个人类的小孩会饿死  还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:14.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  那个小孩不是管理对象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:18.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的职责只有管理森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,我找到爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,禁止你之后的跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,若再尝试接近  我将会强制排除你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,立刻离开这座森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:53.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,你本来不在我的管理下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,摄取完之后就离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,摄取？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,咬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:22.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类的小孩  我理解了你不想离开森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  至少说明下理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:30.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为别人说外面很危险所以不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是谁的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,你原先在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的名字是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:42.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样什么也解决不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,那你的父母在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不明白这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,不明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,话语的意义能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是没有共感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,守护人只会根据规定好的事件行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,并管理森林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:16.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,是只为了森林而存活的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,不寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆没有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,因此只会一个人在森林徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们会一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:45.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:46.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,枷锁的声音会让野兽警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,这句话是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,我去抓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:23.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:29.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:46.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是爸爸的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:59.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是脱落下来的  没有问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不要爸爸坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,你该适可而止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,那不会再接合上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:11.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,比起这个  你该反省下溺死的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的行动是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:18.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的活动时间所剩无几
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:42.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,我消失后  这个人类在森林里生存下去的可能性极低
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,要离开森林？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:50.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,要将你送回人类身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,现在处于温暖时期也能旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,关于你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  那只野兽的名字是「深绿索玛丽」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:10.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,是它最先找到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:13.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:21.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,借用它的名字  从今天开始你就叫做索玛丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:22.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,对  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就是我和索玛丽的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,以及踏上旅途原委
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:46.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆  你剩下的时间还有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:54.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话  能让我看看你现在的身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,表皮只剩下这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,内部的肉出现了龟裂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,体液也在流失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,一个月前  关节处也开始咯吱响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,往后  如果我的身体崩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,我希望把索玛丽托付给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,我很乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:31.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是  你觉得这样就好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,拖着残破不堪的身躯走到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,只是因为义务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,和索玛丽踏上旅途后  现在我才懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,其实原因  从最开始就很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:51.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,我只是想一直看着她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,那么就不能够放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:02.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,其实这之后  你也想待在她的身边守护着她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:24.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,要不要再去睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,一大早就这么没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,喝口茶醒个神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,是从今天开始吧  当旅馆的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  约定好了七天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:50.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,工作是惩治品行不端的客人  就我们两个人做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,饭做好了  想吃了就吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃完记得打扫房间  别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,本来我是想留下来看家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,我会照看索玛丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽经常不顾左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:16.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,眼前要是有好奇的事物就会冲上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,希望你注意一下不要让她摔着了撞着了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有  关于喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,她不喜欢带有苦涩味道的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是也要考虑到营养均衡  不能妥协
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,这些够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是的  这也太保护过度了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:40.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事的  交给锡佐我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,赶紧赶紧  一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,十分不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,锡佐  雪好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:10.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆他们去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,对哦  说是要去当保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以今天你和我留下来看家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,赶紧来吃早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃完过后索玛丽打算干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽想…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,平时都是和爸爸玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:43.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:45.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想送爸爸礼物  感谢平时对我的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,挺不错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是要对爸爸保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,礼物  礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:04.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,送爸爸  礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,礼物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,完成啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:16.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,完成了吗  画像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,遇到麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,我觉得挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,挺不错是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,必须要100满分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,换成其它的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,其它的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,一起边打扫卫生边想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么啊  迎接方式这么夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,才不夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:53.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:58.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,第一次分别了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,话说真是太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,客人们的吵架稀松平常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃霸王餐的还有偷东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,还好我们是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是只有我可忙不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,多亏了你们俩  还给发了工资
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,反而还挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,你好意思说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,店主说明天会送物资到我们这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,物资  是食物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:35.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为下雪购买东西太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,反正是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:42.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,麻烦你们接收一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,今天的卫生弄得真马虎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,明天弄好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,有没有好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事吧  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,在想事情没注意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:26.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,工具也齐全  来编织东西吧  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是索玛丽不会编织…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,没关系  我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,那好  我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过要编织什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,昨天说的物资吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,来了  你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,你就是他们说的小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:55.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个…我已经成年了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:58.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,小孩子是在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,哎呀不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,我是店主的妻子罗扎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,你们可以叫我罗扎阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,这么多  可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:16.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,可以的  丈夫昨天可是夸赞你们帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以你们多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,咦  是在编织什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽想给送礼物给她爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是还在想该送什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,手环怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:36.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,手环作为编织物很畅销的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们店里也有在卖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,被称作是最幸运的手镯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,饱含着制作者祝愿幸福的寓意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  索玛丽能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:58.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,有一种叫三色编的  连小孩子都能够轻松编织
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,来挑选三个喜欢的颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,那  这个和这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,然后将三色的毛线扎起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,右边的放到中间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,之后将左边的线放在上边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,最后在内部相交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,不断重复就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,很简单对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,慢慢地不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,不断将毛线交错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,好厉害  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆肯定也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:41.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:46.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,包含的情感越是强烈  就编织得越是结实哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以要好好地编织
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我会好好地编织
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,罗扎阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,也教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,你要选什么颜色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,亚巴希你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,这些话从哪儿学来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,看上去挺兴奋的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,发生什么了吗  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:43.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,什么都没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是难得一见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,那家伙肯定能买很多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是在耍我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:00.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:04.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就是人类的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:22.98,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:22.98,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比较着并排的影子相视而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.55,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.55,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕阳甩在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:37.62,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:37.62,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘风而去的是那小小的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:44.65,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:44.65,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什么是永远  什么是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:49.25,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:49.25,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我还一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:23:01.53,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:23:01.53,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道当我抬头仰望你时  你的侧脸总是那么地闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:07.88,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:07.88,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牵着手传递的这份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:12.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:12.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论何时都在给予我爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:18.29,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:18.29,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}这不断溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:24.06,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:24.06,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到传达到给你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:32.61,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}交わした約束進もう  未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:32.61,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}向着共同许下的诺言和未来  前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:40.94,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)\blur5\pos(1512.8,1066.4)}守护之人与敌对之人
